<h1>Found a pet?</h1>

<%= link_to 'Check out our listings of missing pets',  post_index%>

<p>What to do: <%= link_to " (More Info)", "http://www.americanhumane.org/animals/adoption-pet-care/caring-for-your-pet/if-you-find-a-lost-pet.html"%></p>
<ol>
<li>Capture and contain it with care</li>
<li>Call the authorities</li>
<li>Check for ID</li>
<li>Get the pet scanned for a microchip</li>
<li>Take pets with no ID to an animal shelter</li>
<li>Post fliers <%= link_to ' (Create flier here)', found_form_path%></li>
</ol>



